title: Prosecutor Announces Charges Against Suspect in Pelosi Attack
description: David DePape, who is accused of breaking into the San Francisco home of Speaker Nancy Pelosi, was charged with attempting to kidnap Ms. Pelosi and with assaulting a relative of a federal official.
dc:creator: The Associated Press

media:content.media:description: Police closed a street near the Pelosi residence in San Francisco as they investigated the scene on Friday.
